race.comment: COMPUTER MAN (3) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only 0.8 lengths from the winner Skedaddle Percy in third(22.13) at this track. Sure to be about the mark. POSSIBLE (2) was a Mix winner two back at this track then although missed the placings finished on the winners' heels when fourth (22.40) at this track. Can find the frame this time. HARPER (7) turned in a solid run last start over 375m at this track finishing 4th and beaten only one length (22.11). Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from six starts. Key player if finds best. INTRODUCED (1) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.
